node.text:
We are proud of the work @yprcla is doing in Black and Brown communities. Healing is a long journey. You’re not alone! How do you take care of yourself? 

@yprcla offers free quality resources to the community. Learn more about YPRC at www.yprcla.org 

Link in bio to learn more about the Yetunde Price Resource Center, created to honor the life and memory of my oldest sister, Yetunde. 

#mentalhealthmatters #youarenotalone #selfcarematters #yprcla

node.text: Between tennis, @elevenbyvenus, chasing Harry and equal pay for women, I’m always on the move! Taking on the world takes @clifbar energy. The more you move, the more the world moves with you. #LetsMovetheWorld
